    "text": "Skip to content\nLOGIN\n\nINVESTOR SOLUTIONS\nPOLICY GUIDELINES\nRESOURCES & BLOG\nCOMPLIANCE\nABOUT US\nPUBLIC COMPANY SOLUTIONS\nCONTACT US\nThe Proxinvest Policy guidelines encourage publicly listed companies in Europe to improve their practices over the long term\nLEARN MORE\nGlass Lewis Acquires French Proxy Advisor Proxinvest\nNEW\nViewpoint®\nOur industry-leading proxy vote management service, elevating the user experience for over 10 years.\nRead more\nProxy Paper®\nExpert analysis, accurate data, and contextual voting recommendations for all the companies in your portfolio.\nRead more\nShare Recall™\nAdvance notification and materiality scores to help you identify important meetings in time to recall lent shares.\nRead more\nRight Claim™\nThe most comprehensive, fully-outsourced solution to manage your global class action settlement filings and ensure maximum recoveries.\nRead more\nPublic Company Resources\nDeliver your company’s unfiltered opinion on Glass Lewis research directly to investor vote decision-makers. Include it in our Proxy Paper with a Report Feedback Statement.\nWe are committed to engaging transparently with companies. Access resources for public companies, learn more about our policies and methodologies and find out how to contact us.\nAccess to the same data, analytics and equity models used by our research team to evaluate executive compensation and inform our investor customers’ custom voting policies.\nContact us today to discuss your governance needs.  Contact Us Today!\nExciting News from Glass Lewis\nGlass Lewis Announces the Acquisition of French Proxy Advisor Proxinvest\nGlass Lewis announces the acquisition of French proxy advisory firm Proxinvest as it [...]\nGlass Lewis Launches SaaS Engagement Management Platform Enabling Investors to Centralize Active Ownership Engagement Data\nGlass Lewis announces the launch of the Engagement Management Platform, enabling investors to [...]\nGlass Lewis and BitSight Partner to